The Telegraph - Calcutta : Nation

 Pritam film

 Shimla, Jan. 14 (PTI): Actress Deepti Naval is making a film on late writer Amrita Pritam that will touch on unknown facts of her life.

 Naval has selected several locations in Himachal Pradeshs Mandi district for the film, the shooting of which is scheduled to start next month.

 Scholar Saini Ashesh, who is assisting Naval in preparing the films script, is tracing certain undisclosed facts about the author of Pinjar.

 Ashesh said in a statement that the movie would cover the initial days of Pritams relationship with lyricist Sahir Ludhianvi and painter Imroz.

 Ashesh is tipped to play Imroz and actress Pratyaksha will play Pritam in her youth.




